HEADWORD: Actionable
<hw>Ac"tion*a*ble</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. LL.
<ets>actionabilis</ets>. See <er>Action</er>.]</ety> <def>That may be
the subject of an action or suit at law; <as>as, to call a man a thief
is <ex>actionable</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

